## Project layout

```
market_terminal/
в”ңв”Җ main.py                        # Entry point
в”ңв”Җ requirements.txt
в”ңв”Җ pyproject.toml
в”ңв”Җ .env.example
в”ңв”Җ src/
в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ market_terminal/
в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җ config/
в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ settings.py           # All config, watchlists, constants
в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җ storage/
в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ database.py           # SQLite schema + migrations
в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ cache.py              # Thread-safe in-memory cache singleton
в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җ enrich/
в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ scorer.py             # VADER + FinBERT scoring
в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ entities.py           # SpaCy NER + regex entity extraction
в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җ ingest/
в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ feeds.py              # RSS, NewsAPI, yfinance, FRED ingestion
в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ aggregator.py         # Score roll-ups + alert detection
в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җ analytics/
в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ engine.py             # Correlation, lead/lag, regime, Bayesian
в”Ӯ     в””в”Җ ui/
в”Ӯ        в””в”Җ app.py                # Textual TUI + background threads
в”ңв”Җ tests/
в”ңв”Җ scripts/
в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ init_db.py
в””в”Җ data/
```

